2026-07-15 18:08:41,670 | INFO | downloader_agent | YouTube download completed successfully: {'video_path': 'D:\\ThinkNext Practice\\2026-latest-project\\Project Raven\\raven\\projects\\raven_1784119100049\\source.mp4', 'title': 'Rain in Chia’s Garden – An Evening of Gentle Showers (雨のやさしい夕暮れ) | Lofi Piano & Cozy Anime Ambience', 'description': 'Welcome back to CHIA’s Garden, where every sound carries a story.\n\n“Rain in Chia’s Garden (雨のやさしい夕暮れ)” captures the magic of a small countryside village as a soft rain begins to fall.\nYou’ll hear tender piano notes, warm ambient pads, and the calming rhythm of raindrops touching wooden rooftops.\n\nThis track paints the feeling of sitting by the window with warm light behind you, watching the world turn silver and quiet.\nIt’s peaceful, nostalgic, and perfect for winding down after a long day.\n\n✨ Perfect for: studying, relaxing, reading, evening calm, background focus\n🎹 Composition: CHIA\n🌧️ Atmosphere: anime-style watercolor rain, soft and warm\n\n🇯🇵 Description (JP):\n\nチアの庭へようこそ。\n\n**「雨のやさしい夕暮れ」**は、田舎の小さな村に静かに降る雨の温かさを描いた曲です。\nピアノのやわらかな音色、木の屋根を叩く雨音、夕暮れのしっとりとした空気が心をほぐします。\n\n窓辺に座り、外の雨を眺めながら過ごす、あの静かなひととき。\nどこか懐かしくて、やさしく包み込む時間をお届けします。\n\n\n#ChiasGarden #LofiRain #AnimeRainAmbience #GhibliVibes #RainyMood #LofiPiano #CalmMusic #RelaxingRain #CozyAnime #RainSounds #JapaneseCountryside #EveningCalm #SoftPiano #RelaxingAmbience #StudyMusic #RainyLofi #ChiaNoNiwa', 'duration': 227.0, 'captions_available': True, 'captions_path': 'D:\\ThinkNext Practice\\2026-latest-project\\Project Raven\\raven\\projects\\raven_1784119100049\\source.en.vtt', 'resolution': '1920x1080'}
